The paper deals with image forensics and specifically focuses on detecting GAN-generated imagery. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper deals with the problem of disinformation campaigns, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves analyzing the structure of the generating network, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
